By ended the story with a idea of retaking an test under the spring, the author set the feeling of starting fresh and perserverence . for example , when the author says� when the snow melts and the geese return and the hibiscus is budding ,�she showed the idea of starting an fresh new life in the spring by returning to their home and the hibiscus is starting fresh by  budding again. This is why spring are when saeng wanted to start fresh and retaken a test. The paragraphs also showing where saeng, liked the hibiscus, is perservering. The hibiscus were perservering by making them under the winter and blooming again during saeng   is perservering by retaken the test. The author ends with this paragraph to show that saeng is not went to given up. 

